---
title: Sticky Korean Chicken & Corn Slaw with Fried Egg
description: This chicken breast is dressing to impress anyone who sits at your table. A rainbow slaw tossed with the sweet and smokey taste of
charred sweetcorn holds up the succulent Korean stir-fry sauced beef. Don’t forget the jewel in the ensemble, the fried egg to top it all off.
